{"type":"message","id":"382fddf4","parentId":"80e8ea2d","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:34:46.124Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Both frontend and backend are running. Let me now also set up a startup script for convenience, and also verify the full deployment works. Let me also check if the app is accessible via the browser.","thinkingSignature":"2f81dad4f1a0a7399ecb4517a903646119bafb28f3f35e58bb94e2f9bbdea9ad"},{"type":"text","text":"前端运行在 `http://localhost:8080` ✅。创建便捷启动脚本：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_6i87tvcsdft4_1","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/bin/bash\n# CodexPool 启动脚本\n# 用法: ./start-codexpool.sh\n\nset -e\n\nAPP_DIR=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/codexpool\"\nLOG_DIR=\"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/logs\"\n\n# 确保 MySQL 在运行\nif ! mysql -u root -e \"SELECT 1\" > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"[CodexPool] MySQL 未运行，正在启动...\"\n    brew services start mysql\n    sleep 2\nfi\n\n# 启动后端\nif ! curl -s http://localhost:3001/api/accounts > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 启动后端服务 (localhost:3001)...\"\n    cd \"$APP_DIR\"\n    node server/index.js >> \"$LOG_DIR/codexpool-server.log\" 2>&1 &\n    sleep 2\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 后端已启动\"\nelse\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 后端服务已在运行\"\nfi\n\n# 启动前端\nif ! curl -s http://localhost:8080 > /dev/null 2>&1; then\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 启动前端服务 (localhost:8080)...\"\n    cd \"$APP_DIR\"\n    npm run dev >> \"$LOG_DIR/codexpool-frontend.log\" 2>&1 &\n    sleep 3\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 前端已启动\"\nelse\n    echo \"[CodexPool] 前端服务已在运行\"\nfi\n\necho \"\"\necho \"✅ CodexPool 已启动\"\necho \"   前端: http://localhost:8080\"\necho \"   后端: http://localhost:3001\"\necho \"   管理面板: http://localhost:8080 (在右侧边栏添加账号)\"\n","file_path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/start-codexpool.sh"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":15702,"output":493,"cacheRead":24939,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41134,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774085675929}}
