{"type":"message","id":"e45d85f6","parentId":"c2b4cc8e","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:36:15.007Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The commit was successful. Now let me report the deployment completion to the user.","thinkingSignature":"8d720783f3b07a3637fff3cfdcfde9552fe5ca3edbf8772df9c7a64f456a9a8a"},{"type":"text","text":"✅ **CodexPool 部署完成！**\n\n### 部署摘要\n\n| 项目 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| **仓库** | https://github.com/heyuqiu2023/CodexPool |\n| **位置** | `/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/apps/codexpool` |\n| **前端** | ✅ 运行在 `http://localhost:8080` |\n| **后端** | ✅ 运行在 `http://localhost:3001` |\n| **数据库** | ✅ MySQL 9.6.0, 数据库 `codex_pool_manager` |\n| **启动脚本** | ✅ `scripts/start-codexpool.sh` |\n\n### 功能特性\n- **多账号管理** — 添加和切换多个 Codex 账号（ChatGPT OAuth）\n- **实时监控** — 显示 5 小时窗口和每周配额使用情况\n- **自动轮换** — 5 小时使用率超过 90% 时自动切换账号\n- **智能轮询** — 根据使用级别调整检查频率（30min → 10min → 5min）\n- **活动日志** — 实时日志流，记录轮换事件和使用检查\n\n### 访问方式\n- 打开浏览器访问：**http://localhost:8080**\n- 在右侧边栏点击 **+ Add Account** 添加账号\n\n### 便捷启动\n以后可以用这个命令一键启动：\n```bash\n./scripts/start-codexpool.sh\n```\n\n---\n\n⚠️ **注意**：day1-3 均值回归信号模块任务已被此部署请求中断，任务状态已记录到 `checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md`。需要时可以继续执行超额收益过滤（excess_ret5）等优化。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":77744,"output":370,"cacheRead":24939,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103053,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774085732913}}
