{"type":"message","id":"645a7b37","parentId":"5e4dae96","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:40:15.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to do the actual evaluation work: assess the next round of rule enhancements. Let me think about what improvements could be made:\n\n1. **信号打分精度**: \n   - Currently using simple percentile ranks\n   - Could try z-score normalization to make scores more comparable across days\n   - Could run IC (Information Coefficient) analysis to validate factor effectiveness\n\n2. **候选股质量**:\n   - Could add volume trend filter (avoid stocks with declining volume)\n   - Could add fundamental filters (avoid stocks with deteriorating fundamentals)\n\n3. **市场宽度计算**:\n   - Currently using simple MA20 breadth\n   - Could add more sophisticated breadth metrics\n\nLet me do a deeper analysis and present findings to the user.","thinkingSignature":"d2aa000f25105da5706c5823831cb851765d513590a273c503b283bb99fff932"},{"type":"text","text":"### 📊 day1-3 候选股质量评估结果\n\n| 指标 | 结果 | 状态 |\n|------|------|------|\n| excess_ret5 范围 | -16.52% ~ -1.70% | ✅ 全部跑输HS300 |\n| range_pos20 | 10.11% ~ 54.33% | ✅ 全部处低位 |\n| Top3 仓位集中度 | 13.66% | ✅ 分散度良好 |\n| 分数标准差 | 0.353 | ⚠️ 可提升区分度 |\n\n---\n\n### 🔍 下一轮补强方向评估\n\n基于当前质量分析，建议优先推进以下三项：\n\n#### 1️⃣ 信号打分精度增强\n- **现状**：百分位排名（rank percentile），各因子权重手工设定\n- **问题**：rank 无法捕捉因子强度差异（大跌10%与跌5%分数相同）\n- **方案**：改为 **z-score 标准化** + **IC权重动态调整**\n  ```python\n  # 替代方案示例\n  from scipy import stats\n  z_dist_ma10 = stats.zscore(df['dist_ma10'])  # 均值回归，越负越好\n  z_ret5 = stats.zscore(df['ret5'])\n  z_excess = stats.zscore(df['excess_ret5'])\n  df['score'] = w1*z_dist + w2*z_ret5 + w3*z_excess  # 可比较强度\n  ```\n\n#### 2️⃣ 候选股质量增强\n- **现状**：仅技术面过滤，无基本面门控\n- **风险**：可能选入基本面恶化的超跌股（\"跌势未尽\"）\n- **方案**：增加 **成交额趋势过滤**（避免缩量下跌股）\n  ```python\n  # 5日均额 vs 20日均额，过滤额量背离\n  amount_ratio = amount_ma5 / amount_ma20\n  # amount_ratio < 0.5 → 缩量下跌，剔除\n  ```\n\n#### 3️⃣ 市场宽度计算升级\n- **现状**：MA20 价格宽度单一指标\n- **方案**：综合三个宽度指标做加权判断\n  - A股上涨家数/总交易家数（官方 breadth）\n  - 科创50 + 创业板综 加权趋势\n  - Macd 柱状图方向\n\n---\n\n请问你希望优先推进哪一项？或者三项都做？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43593,"output":669,"cacheRead":24939,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69201,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774085996876}}
