{"type":"message","id":"b4f4e62b","parentId":"c912c5ac","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:40:45.715Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The history CSV has an `amount` column. I can compute amount_ma5 and amount_ma20 from it. Now let me modify the script to:\n\n1. Compute `amount_ma5` and `amount_ma20` as rolling means of amount\n2. Compute `amount_ratio = amount_ma5 / amount_ma20` (大于1表示放量，缩量则<1）\n3. Filter out stocks with amount_ratio < 0.5 (缩量下跌通常是陷阱)\n4. Update the config with new parameters\n\nLet me do the modifications now.","thinkingSignature":"2437500169d23c5d59fe6588851ea0f1761439ed1763704b6ddb4116b49707a6"},{"type":"text","text":"amount 字段存在。现在修改脚本，添加成交额趋势过滤：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9vme6xb5i34m_1","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py","oldText":"    # Compute ret5 using pivot on recent data\n    recent = df[df[\"trade_date\"] <= trade_date].groupby(\"ts_code\").tail(6).sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n    piv = recent.pivot(index=\"trade_date\", columns=\"ts_code\", values=\"close\")\n    if len(piv) >= 6:\n        ret5 = (piv.iloc[-1] / piv.iloc[-6] - 1).to_dict()\n        latest[\"ret5\"] = latest[\"ts_code\"].map(ret5)\n    else:\n        latest[\"ret5\"] = np.nan","new_string":"    # Compute ret5 using pivot on recent data\n    recent = df[df[\"trade_date\"] <= trade_date].groupby(\"ts_code\").tail(6).sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n    piv = recent.pivot(index=\"trade_date\", columns=\"ts_code\", values=\"close\")\n    if len(piv) >= 6:\n        ret5 = (piv.iloc[-1] / piv.iloc[-6] - 1).to_dict()\n        latest[\"ret5\"] = latest[\"ts_code\"].map(ret5)\n    else:\n        latest[\"ret5\"] = np.nan\n\n    # Compute amount_ma5 and amount_ma20 for volume trend filter\n    amt_recent = df[df[\"trade_date\"] <= trade_date].groupby(\"ts_code\").tail(25).sort_values([\"ts_code\", \"trade_date\"])\n    g_amt = amt_recent.groupby(\"ts_code\", group_keys=False)\n    amt_recent[\"amt_ma5\"] = g_amt[\"amount\"].transform(lambda s: s.rolling(5, min_periods=3).mean())\n    amt_recent[\"amt_ma20\"] = g_amt[\"amount\"].transform(lambda s: s.rolling(20, min_periods=10).mean())\n    amt_latest = amt_recent[amt_recent[\"trade_date\"] == trade_date][[\"ts_code\", \"amt_ma5\", \"amt_ma20\"]].copy()\n    latest = latest.merge(amt_latest, on=\"ts_code\", how=\"left\")\n    latest[\"amount_ratio\"] = (latest[\"amt_ma5\"] / latest[\"amt_ma20\"].replace(0, np.nan)).clip(lower=0).fillna(1.0)"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":43596,"output":710,"cacheRead":24939,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":69245,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774086031288}}
