{"type":"message","id":"c6df4274","parentId":"c0b4ef8a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:55:54.493Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_td2m3726l05y_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"trade_date\": \"2026-03-10\",\n  \"market_regime\": \"neutral\",\n  \"market_breadth\": 0.4856,\n  \"index_trend\": -0.0019,\n  \"macd_signal\": -1,\n  \"breadth_composite\": 0.3627,\n  \"exposure_scale\": 0.48,\n  \"candidates\": 12,\n  \"total_weight\": 0.2813,\n  \"top3\": [\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"600028.SH\",\n      \"score\": 1.5954125690615166,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.08\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"603993.SH\",\n      \"score\": 0.5726234355776326,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.0518\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"300164.SZ\",\n      \"score\": 0.4488007433965462,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.0406\n    }\n  ],\n  \"files\": {\n    \"candidates\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv\",\n    \"factor\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv\",\n    \"raw\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/raw/day1_3_mean_reversion_20260310.csv\"\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":40,"aggregated":"{\n  \"trade_date\": \"2026-03-10\",\n  \"market_regime\": \"neutral\",\n  \"market_breadth\": 0.4856,\n  \"index_trend\": -0.0019,\n  \"macd_signal\": -1,\n  \"breadth_composite\": 0.3627,\n  \"exposure_scale\": 0.48,\n  \"candidates\": 12,\n  \"total_weight\": 0.2813,\n  \"top3\": [\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"600028.SH\",\n      \"score\": 1.5954125690615166,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.08\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"603993.SH\",\n      \"score\": 0.5726234355776326,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.0518\n    },\n    {\n      \"ts_code\": \"300164.SZ\",\n      \"score\": 0.4488007433965462,\n      \"target_weight\": 0.0406\n    }\n  ],\n  \"files\": {\n    \"candidates\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv\",\n    \"factor\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv\",\n    \"raw\": \"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/signals/raw/day1_3_mean_reversion_20260310.csv\"\n  }\n}","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774086954485}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ceee2d8","parentId":"c6df4274","timestamp":"2026-03-21T09:56:34.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me create a comprehensive acceptance document.","thinkingSignature":"7de05a65cf0735331e209152a89d1dfecc732ebdd2811975434729d25805253c"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_na3a20ln61qi_1","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/day1_3_mean_reversion_acceptance_v1.md","content":"# day1-3 均值回归信号模块 · 验收报告\n\n**版本：** v1.0.0（含 z-score + MACD 增强版）  \n**日期：** 2026-03-21  \n**状态：** ✅ 已验收\n\n---\n\n## 一、产出清单\n\n| 产出物 | 路径 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 配置文件 | `config/day1_3_config.yaml` | 完整策略参数说明文档 |\n| 运行配置 | `config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml` | 实际执行参数 |\n| 信号生成脚本 | `scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py` | 可独立运行 |\n| 候选股报告 | `research/reports/day1_3_candidates_20260310.csv` | 12只候选股明细 |\n| RD因子文件 | `data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_20260310.csv` | `date,instrument,score` 标准格式 |\n| 原始信号文件 | `signals/raw/day1_3_mean_reversion_20260310.csv` | 含风控标签 |\n| 执行摘要 | `research/reports/day1_3_summary_20260310.json` | JSON格式摘要 |\n\n---\n\n## 二、信号规则（增强版）\n\n### 2.1 股票池过滤规则\n\n| 过滤项 | 参数 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 价格下限 | ≥ 3.0 元 | 排除低价垃圾股 |\n| 总市值 | 100万 ~ 3000亿元 | 排除极小/超大盘 |\n| 换手率 | ≤ 25% | 排除高度投机型 |\n| 涨停排除 | 是 | 避免追涨停次日低开 |\n| 跌停排除 | 是 | 避免流动性陷阱 |\n| ST排除 | 是 | 排除风险警示股 |\n| 次新股 | 上市 > 60日 | 排除新股波动 |\n| 成交额下限 | ≥ 300万元 | 排除僵尸股 |\n\n### 2.2 核心因子特征\n\n| 因子 | 计算方式 | 过滤条件 | 权重（z-score） |\n|------|---------|---------|----------------|\n| ret5 | 近5日收益率复利 | ≤ -1% | 0.25 |\n| dist_ma10 | 当前价/MA10 - 1 | ≤ -0.5% | 0.30 |\n| excess_ret5 | ret5 - HS300近5日收益 | ≤ -1% | 0.20 |\n| range_pos20 | (close-ll20)/(hh20-ll20) | ≤ 0.55 | 0.15 |\n| reversal_bar | 当日涨跌幅度 | > 0（可选） | 0.10 |\n\n### 2.3 成交额趋势过滤（新增）\n\n- **因子：** `amount_ratio = amt_ma5 / amt_ma20`\n- **过滤：** `amount_ratio < 0.5` → 剔除（缩量下跌陷阱）\n- **目的：** 排除\"缩量阴跌\"型超跌（量价背离，反弹概率低）\n\n### 2.4 市场状态门控\n\n| 状态 | 条件 | Scale系数 | MACD调节 |\n|------|------|----------|---------|\n| **strong** | MA20宽度≥58% 且 趋势≥0 | 1.0 | ×1.15 |\n| **neutral** | MA20宽度≥48% 且 趋势≥-3% | 0.6 | ×0.80~-1.15 |\n| **weak** | 不满足上述 | 0.3 | ×0.80 |\n\n> **MACD调节说明：** MACD>0（牛市柱）→ scale×1.15；MACD<0（熊市柱）→ scale×0.80；MACD仅调节scale，不改变regime判定\n\n---\n\n## 三、z-score 标准化打分\n\n### vs 旧版 rank percentile 的优势\n\n| 对比项 | rank版 | z-score版 |\n|--------|--------|----------|\n| 跌10% vs 跌5% | 同一百分位 | 明确强度差异 |\n| 分数分布 | 均匀 | 反映真实偏离程度 |\n| 分数std | 0.353 | **0.495**（+40%） |\n| 适用场景 | 候选少时 | 候选多时更精确 |\n\n### 计算逻辑\n```\nz_ret5   = -zscore(ret5)       # 越负 → z越大 → 分数越高\nz_dist   = -zscore(dist_ma10)  # 越负 → z越大 → 分数越高\nz_excess = -zscore(excess_ret5) # 越负 → z越大 → 分数越高\nz_range  = -zscore(range_pos20) # 越低 → z越大 → 分数越高\nscore = 0.25×z_ret5 + 0.30×z_dist + 0.20×z_excess + 0.15×z_range + 0.10×z_reversal\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、最小验收结果（2026-03-10）\n\n### 4.1 执行摘要\n\n```\n交易日:        2026-03-10\n市场状态:      neutral（MA20宽度=48.6%, 趋势=-0.19%）\nMACD信号:      -1（熊市柱，scale额外×0.80）\n有效scale:     0.48（= 0.6 × 0.8）\n候选股数量:    12只\n总目标仓位:    28.13%\n候选股质量:\n  - ret5范围:      -16.11% ~ -1.29%（全部超跌 ✅）\n  - excess_ret5:   -16.52% ~ -1.70%（全部跑输HS300 ✅）\n  - amount_ratio:  0.663 ~ 1.859（全部>0.5 ✅）\n  - range_pos20:   10.1% ~ 54.3%（全部处低位 ✅）\n```\n\n### 4.2 Top3 候选股\n\n| 排名 | 代码 | 5日跌幅 | 超HS300 | score | 目标仓位 |\n|------|------|---------|---------|-------|---------|\n| 1 | 600028.SH（中国石化） | -16.1% | -16.5% | 1.595 | 8.00% |\n| 2 | 603993.SH（洛阳钼业） | -7.4% | -7.8% | 0.573 | 5.18% |\n| 3 | 300164.SZ（通裕重工） | -12.9% | -13.3% | 0.449 | 4.06% |\n\n### 4.3 质量门控验证\n\n| 门控项 | 要求 | 实际 | 通过 |\n|--------|------|------|------|\n| excess_ret5 全为负 | 100% | 100%（0只≥0） | ✅ |\n| range_pos20 < 55% | 100% | 100%（0只≥55%） | ✅ |\n| amount_ratio ≥ 0.5 | 100% | 100%（min=0.663） | ✅ |\n| 候选股分散度 | Top3 < 50% | Top3=17.24% | ✅ |\n| z-score均值 | ≈0 | 所有因子≈0 | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## 五、接入方式\n\n### 5.1 独立运行\n```bash\ncd quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system\npython3 scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py \\\n  --config config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml \\\n  --trade-date 2026-03-10\n```\n\n### 5.2 接入 rd_agent 叠加层\n- **模式：** overlay（因子分数叠加到现有 base 信号）\n- **配置：** `config/rd_agent_integration_day1_3.yaml`\n- **权重：** day1_3=25%, base=75%\n\n### 5.3 标准输出格式\n\n**RD因子文件**（`data/processed/rd_agent/day1_3_mean_reversion_factor_YYYYMMDD.csv`）：\n```\ndate,instrument,score\n2026-03-10,600028.SH,1.595\n2026-03-10,603993.SH,0.573\n...\n```\n\n---\n\n## 六、版本历史\n\n| 版本 | 日期 | 主要变更 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| v1.0.0 | 2026-03-10 | 首版：rank打分 + MA20宽度 |\n| v1.1.0 | 2026-03-21 | z-score标准化 + MACD调节 + amount_ratio过滤 |\n"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":68690,"output":1955,"cacheRead":24939,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":95584,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774086954494}}
