{"type":"message","id":"e4ed7a72","parentId":"d4b21f62","timestamp":"2026-03-21T10:57:15.968Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"<active-task-guard>\nSource: /Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace/checklists/ACTIVE_TASK.md\nStatus: active\nUse this only as the recovery rail for the current multi-step task.\nIf the user's latest message is a continuation, continue from Current, update ACTIVE_TASK.md after each minimum deliverable, and immediately promote the next item.\nIf the user's latest message is clearly unrelated, do not force this task.\n\nGoal:\n- 从零实现 day1-3 风格的 A 股日频均值回归信号模块，并接入现有 personal-a-share-research-system 的信号/回测链路\n\nAcceptance:\n- ✅ 产出新的策略说明或配置文件，明确 day1-3 信号规则、市场状态门控与接入方式\n- ✅ 产出至少一个可运行脚本，能生成标准化 `date,instrument,score` 信号文件或直接进入现有回测链路\n- ✅ 产出一次最小验收结果（脚本运行输出、报告或日志），证明首版实现已能被系统读取/验证\n\nCurrent:\n- 扩展 day1-3 历史因子：生成 2024-2026 两年数据，提升融合回测覆盖率\n\nNext:\n- （无）\n\nRecent Evidence:\n- **验收报告**: `quant_projects/personal-a-share-research-system/research/reports/day1_3_mean_reversion_acceptance_v1.md`\n- **配置文件**: `config/day1_3_config.yaml` + `config/day1_3_mean_reversion.yaml`\n- **运行脚本**: `scripts/generate_day1_3_mean_reversion_signals.py`\n- 2026-03-10: neutral regime, scale=0.48, 12只候选, 28.13%总仓位, 全质量门控通过 ✅\n\nIntegrity Warnings:\n- None\n\nBlockers:\n- None\n</active-task-guard>\n\nSystem: [2026-03-21 18:57:15 GMT+8] Feishu[feishu-assistant] DM | ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7 [msg:om_x100b54d3d6533ca0c30c6a3fbabb20b, reply_to:om_x100b54d3dfe530acc458273ff1bf819]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54d3d6533ca0c30c6a3fbabb20b\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 18:57 GMT+8\",\n  \"has_reply_context\": true\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"n