{"type":"message","id":"5fb586f5","parentId":"20e43d2f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T12:29:14.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user said \"好\" (okay). This seems like a simple acknowledgment. Let me check if there's an active task to continue or if this is just a brief acknowledgment.\n\nLooking at the ACTIVE_TASK.md status from the most recent context, it shows:\n- Status: active\n- Current: 扩展 day1-3 历史因子：生成 2024-2026 两年数据，提升融合回测覆盖率\n- Acceptance: all ✅\n- Next: (无)\n\nAnd the queue file showed P0/P1 items all completed.\n\nThis \"好\" is likely just an acknowledgment of the security report summary I just provided. The user seems satisfied with the report summary. I don't need to do anything specific here unless they ask for more.\n\n\nSince they've acknowledged the report, I'll just mark this as done.","thinkingSignature":"60da12df3df9bb97288efd226848ec010a94efb6fc93899fa446122392bd4e41"},{"type":"text","text":"NO_REPLY"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":145,"output":171,"cacheRead":118019,"cacheWrite":10569,"totalTokens":128904,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774096143737}}
