{"type":"message","id":"70654e39","parentId":"3ee1d78f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:51:49.621Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear security audit result. Let me summarize:\n\n**CRITICAL (1):**\n- `models.small_params`: Small models (gemma3:4b) with sandbox=off and web tools enabled. This is a significant risk - a small model with exec/process/browser access could be exploited via prompt injection.\n\n**WARN (4):**\n1. `channels.feishu.doc_owner_open_id`: Feishu doc creation grants permissions to requesting user\n2. `security.trust_model.multi_user_heuristic`: Multiple users detected with open dmPolicy and allowFrom=[\"*\"]. All 8 agents have sandbox=off with full exec/fs/write access\n\n\n3. `plugins.tools_reachable_permissive_policy`: Extension plugins may be reachable under permissive tool policy\n4. `plugins.installs_unpinned_npm_specs`: openclaw-lark has unpinned npm spec\n\n**INFO:**\n- Gateway bind: loopback only ✅\n- Trust model: personal assistant (single user) ✅\n- Browser control: enabled\n- tools.elevated: enabled\n- hooks.internal: enabled\n\nThe main concern is the gemma3 model running without sandbox protection while having web tool access.\n\nFor the gemma3 model, I should either disable its web capabilities or restrict it to a more controlled sandbox environment. The feishu-assistant and coding-agent accounts both have open policies that allow any user to send direct messages, which is risky if these are exposed to multiple people. All the agents are running with full exec and filesystem access to the entire workspace, which is appropriate for their use case but increases the blast radius if any agent gets compromised. The gemma3 model is the main vulnerability I should address first, followed by reviewing the open dm policies and the unbounded plugin permissions.","thinkingSignature":"5facbf7f3a60549b5b84b9bb76ec00acbb5f4a8e92fd124cd85b2a950c05880d"},{"type":"text","text":"安全审计完成，发现 **1 个严重 + 4 个警告**。汇报并给出加固方案：\n\n---\n\n### 🔴 CRITICAL\n\n| 问题 | 风险 | 建议修复 |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **gemma3:4b 小模型（4B）无沙箱 + 开启 web 工具** | 小模型防御对抗性输入能力弱，若被钓鱼链接攻击可触发 exec/browser | 方案 A：关闭 web 工具（web_search/web_fetch/browser）<br>方案 B：开启 sandbox=all<br>方案 C：仅在使用时开启，用完关闭 |\n\n---\n\n### 🟡 WARN × 4\n\n| 问题 | 风险 | 建议 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **feishu 文档创建权限** | coding-agent/zhidao 发消息可能触发文档创建 | 非必要则关闭 `channels.feishu.tools.doc` |\n| **多用户宽松策略** | feishu-assistant/coding-agent 的 `dmPolicy=open`、`allowFrom=[\"*\"]` | 保留（内部助理需开放），但需确认是内部有限用户 |\n| **插件工具宽松可达** | active-task-guard / openclaw-lark / simple-task-router 在 permissive 策略下可被调用 | 若接收到非信任输入，可切换为 restrictive profiles |\n| **openclaw-lark 未锁定版本** | 供应链稳定风险 | 固定版本 `@larksuite/openclaw-lark@x.y.z` |\n\n---\n\n### 加固方案（按优先级）\n\n| 优先级 | 操作 | 影响 | 可逆性 |\n|--------|------|------|--------|\n| **P0 立即** | gemma3 小模型：关闭 web 工具 | simple agent 无法网页搜索 | ✅ 可改回 |\n| **P1 今天** | 所有 agent 加 `sandbox=require`（执行需明确授权） | exec 需 --sandbox flag 授权 | ✅ 可改回 |\n| **P2 今天** | 固定 openclaw-lark 版本 | 防止自动升级引不稳定 | ⚠️ 需记录版本 |\n| **P3 可选** | `channels.feishu.tools.doc=false`（非必要则关） | 无法通过飞书创建文档 | ⚠️ 需确认不常用 |\n\n---\n\n需要我执行哪个级别的加固？\n\n1. **只修 P0**（gemma3 web 工具关闭）— 最紧急\n2. **P0 + P1**（加 sandbox require）\n3. **全部执行**（含版本固定 + doc 权限）\n4. **先看具体命令**，再决定"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":93140,"output":911,"cacheRead":43165,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137216,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774104677660}}
