{"type":"message","id":"4be56b3a","parentId":"6913f33a","timestamp":"2026-03-21T14:53:37.443Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Good. Now I have all the info I need. Let me plan the changes:\n\n**P0: gemma3 web tools disable**\n- The `simple` agent uses `ollama-local/gemma3:4b` model. \n- The audit says the issue is with `agents.list.simple.model` having `web=[web_fetch, browser]` and `sandbox=off`.\n- I need to either disable web tools globally (via `tools.deny`) or add a per-agent sandbox config.\n- Since there's no top-level `tools` section, I need to add one. Or I can add a per-agent `sandbox` config to the simple agent.\n\n\n- For P1, I need to add a sandbox config to `agents.defaults.sandbox.mode = \"require\"` so all agents must explicitly opt into sandboxing.\n- For P2, I should pin the openclaw-lark spec to an exact version.\n- For P3, I need to disable the doc tool in feishu channels.\n\nLet me start making these changes systematically, beginning with adding the sandbox requirement to defaults.\n\nNow I'm checking the documentation on how to properly configure the tools deny list and sandbox settings - it looks like I can use `tools.deny` to block specific tool groups, and for the gemma3:4b model specifically, I need to ensure sandbox mode is set to \"all\" while disabling web access. Let me apply these configurations now.","thinkingSignature":"c4639326e8408b710eb47bfaba2e0d18d3d7ce9116046b95e1168fbecb26e754"},{"type":"text","text":"好，开始执行四项加固：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_r4ml2g367ita_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 << 'EOF'\nimport json\n\ncfg = json.load(open('/Users/ling/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))\n\n# P0: Add tools deny for web group + sandbox on gemma3 agent\n# Add top-level tools section\ncfg['tools'] = {\n    \"deny\": [\"group:web\", \"browser\"]\n}\n\n# P1: Add agents.defaults.sandbox.mode = \"require\"\ncfg['agents']['defaults']['sandbox'] = {\n    \"mode\": \"require\"\n}\n\n# P2: Pin openclaw-lark to exact version\ninstalls = cfg['plugins']['installs']\ninstalls['openclaw-lark']['spec'] = \"@larksuite/openclaw-lark@2026.3.17\"\n\n# P3: Disable feishu doc tool\ncfg['channels']['feishu']['tools']['doc'] = False\n\n# Save\njson.dump(cfg, open('/Users/ling/.openclaw/openclaw.json', 'w'), indent=2, ensure_ascii=False)\nprint(\"All 4 changes applied\")\nprint(\"P0: tools.deny=['group:web','browser'] added\")\nprint(\"P1: agents.defaults.sandbox.mode='require' added\")\nprint(\"P2: openclaw-lark pinned to @2026.3.17\")\nprint(\"P3: channels.feishu.tools.doc=False\")\nEOF\n2>&1","timeout":5}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":94487,"output":626,"cacheRead":43165,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":138278,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774104800630}}
