{"type":"message","id":"20d1668f","parentId":"02dc32e3","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:54:04.746Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about ChatGPT Team's 5-person plan daily usage limit. Let me think about what I know.\n\nChatGPT Team has:\n- $30/user/month (billed monthly)\n- 100 messages/day per user (in some plans) or higher\n- Or it might be based on usage rather than strict limits\n- Higher limits for Plus members in some contexts\n\nActually, I should be careful here - I'm not 100% certain about the exact current ChatGPT Team plan limits. Let me think about what I know:\n\nChatGPT Plus is $20/month with about 40 messages every 3 hours (varies).\n\n\nChatGPT Team comes with significantly higher usage limits than Plus, but the exact daily caps aren't publicly disclosed and likely vary by region and OpenAI's current policies. I should be honest that I don't have the precise numbers rather than guessing.","thinkingSignature":"a1e1d62b249e373f23d94228a6d72617071b61f819e0c4b30e285606520bd480"},{"type":"text","text":"ChatGPT Team 的具体每日额度**不是固定数字**，官方没有公开精确限制。\n\n大致规律：\n\n| 套餐 | 月费 | 额度 |\n|------|------|------|\n| Plus | $20/人 | 有较严格限制 |\n| Team | $30/人 | **远高于 Plus**，但无固定上限 |\n| Enterprise | 定制 | 无限制，按需 |\n\nTeam 版的核心优势是**更高的并发和更快的响应速度**，而不是固定额度。\n\n---\n\n**说实话：** 关于 Team 具体每人每天能用多少，OpenAI 官方没有公开明确数字，我的知识可能不准确。建议直接到 [chatgpt.com/team](https://chatgpt.com/team) 查看或咨询官方。\n\n---\n\n你实际使用场景是什么？如果只是日常对话或轻量任务，**Plus 或中转站**完全够用；如果需要高频调用或企业级用途，再考虑 Team。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":363,"cacheRead":139927,"cacheWrite":660,"totalTokens":141075,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108431654}}
