{"type":"message","id":"0ebfc042","parentId":"b3cd4830","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:55:27.732Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about whether their current proxy service (中转站) pricing is reasonable. They pay 80 RMB/month and get $200/day in credits. Let me think about this.\n\n$200/day × 30 days = $6000/month worth of API credits for 80 RMB ≈ $11 USD/month.\n\nThis sounds EXTREMELY cheap - like $200/day would normally cost way more than $11/month. Let me think about what this means.\n\nActually, the user says \"每天有200美元的额度\" which could mean they have a $200 daily budget/limit, not necessarily that they're using all of it. But still, 80 RMB for any substantial API access is extremely cheap.\n \nComparing to official pricing, GPT-4o's cost per million tokens is around $2.50 for input and $10 for output, so $200 in API credits would only cover roughly 100K tokens of output per day - that's not actually that generous. But they're only paying 80 RMB (about $11 USD) monthly, which is absurdly cheap for any AI API access, especially if they're actually maxing out $200 daily.\n\nThe legitimacy is questionable - it could be a subsidized educational rate, a gray market setup with cross-subsidies, a亏损营销 strategy, or even something problematic. Either way, it's priced so low that it almost doesn't matter whether I recommend it or not - the value is incredible if it's reliable, and if it's not legitimate, the price point is the least of the concerns.\n\nGiven the context of what we were just discussing about CodexPool, this is likely a coding-focused API access service, which explains why it's so heavily discounted compared to standard OpenAI pricing.","thinkingSignature":"748cade716f9718656424ef8d3ff97c888365403c9eeeedb1dc1f0ec8620a9df"},{"type":"text","text":"这个价格**极低，低到需要警惕**。\n\n简单算一笔账：\n\n| 项目 | 估算 |\n|------|------|\n| 80元/月 | ≈ $11 美元/月 |\n| $200/天额度 | ≈ $6000/月 |\n| 相当于官方 API 的 | **不到 0.2% 的价格** |\n\n---\n\n### 这个价格意味着什么？\n\n**可能性1：** 那是\"优惠价\"或\"邀请制内测价\"，随时可能涨价或跑路\n\n**可能性2：** 二手贩子从教育计划/企业账号拆分出来，有被封号风险\n\n**可能性3：** 确实是正规渠道补贴（极少）\n\n---\n\n### 我的判断\n\n**值不值？** — 如果能稳定用、账号不被封，**超级值**\n\n**靠不靠谱？** — 有风险，建议：\n- 不要依赖它做关键任务\n- 重要数据/账号不要走这个渠道\n- 有心理准备随时失效\n\n---\n\n### 建议\n\n如果你已经有这个渠道，用来做**非关键、非敏感**的日常任务没问题。但核心业务建议还是用官方 API 或更透明的服务。\n\n你现在用的是什么模型/场景？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":589,"cacheRead":140380,"cacheWrite":724,"totalTokens":141818,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108506145}}
{"type":"message","id":"64dba689","parentId":"0ebfc042","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:56:01.635Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-03-21 23:56:01 GMT+8] Feishu[feishu-assistant] DM | ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7 [msg:om_x100b54dfb7c7a8a4c4944abc16953e8]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b54dfb7c7a8a4c4944abc16953e8\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Sat 2026-03-21 23:56 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_83b02a0239e70fc8a4bf0b79aa8f9db7\"\n}\n```\n\n量化投资系统"}],"timestamp":1774108561632}}
{"type":"message","id":"2cc1b1c3","parentId":"64dba689","timestamp":"2026-03-21T15:56:12.844Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is using the relay API service for their quantitative investment system. This is a serious use case - they need reliability and stability for their trading system. Let me give them honest advice about this.","thinkingSignature":"cb26e443a8c82017b1b59cd0af557bcfefc99e3577e08d1a0e741f815942dddb"},{"type":"text","text":"量化投资系统用这个渠道，**风险需要认真评估**：\n\n### ⚠️ 核心问题\n\n| 风险点 | 对量化的影响 |\n|--------|------------|\n| **账号被封** | 交易中断，策略无法执行 |\n| **服务突然失效** | 信号/风控链条断裂，可能造成实际损失 |\n| **数据泄露** | 你的交易策略/持仓数据经过第三方 |\n| **无SLA保障** | 出问题没有赔偿/恢复承诺 |\n\n### 建议\n\n**短期（应急/测试）：** 继续用中转站，但要确保有**备用链路**\n\n**长期（实盘）：** \n- 核心交易、风控建议走官方 API\n- 中转站仅作备用或非关键任务\n\n### 你的情况\n\n你现在有 coding agent（GPT-5.4/GPT-5.3）和 OpenClaw 主链路，建议：\n- **coding agent** → 中转站没问题（非核心）\n- **实盘量化系统** → 考虑官方 API + 备用机制\n\n---\n\n需要我帮你规划一个官方 API + 中转站的双链路备份方案吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":278,"cacheRead":140955,"cacheWrite":708,"totalTokens":142066,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774108561634}}
