{"type":"message","id":"a3896ae8","parentId":"cdd66b5f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:28:28.917Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants option A: Install to OpenClaw workspace so the rules/skills/commands take effect as coding enhancements.\n\nThis is similar to the xu-xiang fork we read earlier (same upstream repo \"everything-claude-code\"). This is the Chinese version (seablue1985). We already read the security audit and it was flagged as a security concern - but this is the user's own fork.\n\nHowever, based on USER.md: \"安装任何新 skill 前，必须先用 clawsec 做安全检查\". I should run a security check first before installing.\n\nAlso, this is a complex system with many components. Let me think about what \"installing to OpenClaw workspace\" means:\n\n\n1. It's not a skill that can be installed via clawhub\n2. It contains rules, commands, skills, agents, hooks - essentially a full AI agent configuration system\n3. Installing it to workspace would mean copying the relevant files into the workspace\n\nBut wait - this is a full configuration system (50K+ stars), not a simple skill. Installing it would require understanding what it does and how it integrates. Plus there's the security risk: we already flagged this repo's upstream (xu-xiang fork) as having security concerns. This is the user's own fork, but the security implications are still relevant.\n\nLet me think about the right approach here. This is a complex full AI agent configuration system with rules, skills, commands, hooks, and agents. It's much more involved than a typical skill install, and there are known security concerns with the upstream. I should clarify what they actually want to accomplish - do they want the coding rules, the skills, or the full system integrated into OpenClaw?\n\nFor the coding rules specifically, I could add the rules directory to their agents config, though that requires understanding the format. For skills, I'd use clawhub. For the full system, that's a much bigger undertaking. Let me ask what their main goal is so I can propose the right approach.\n\nActually, looking at this more carefully - the everything-claude-code repo is a comprehensive AI coding system with a rules directory (language-specific rules in TypeScript/Python/Go/Java), skills, commands, hooks, and agents. The safest path would be installing via clawhub if available, or manually copying specific rules. But since they said \"A\" and want to install to OpenClaw workspace, I need to understand what they're actually trying to accomplish first.\n\nGiven the complexity and the security concerns we already raised, I should ask what specific part they want to deploy and whether they've considered the security implications of a fork from a security-audited repo.","thinkingSignature":"2a01207b744c62fbc8770bc3254ef1eb6433d6c62c180798ae0f832e885a80f4"},{"type":"text","text":"安装这个系统比较复杂（涉及 rules/skills/commands/hooks 多层配置），而且这是之前安全审计报告的同源仓库（everything-claude-code），在安装前需要确认几点：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lg1oyp72lvun_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -sL --max-time 15 \"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/seablue1985/everything-claude-code-zh/refs/heads/main/README.zh-CN.md\" 2>&1 | head -80","yieldMs":13000,"timeout":15}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":125,"output":673,"cacheRead":141946,"cacheWrite":1163,"totalTokens":143907,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774114092919}}
{"type":"message","id":"0e99a7d7","parentId":"a3896ae8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:28:29.708Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_lg1oyp72lvun_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Everything Claude Code\n\n[![Stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/affaan-m/everything-claude-code?style=flat)](https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code/stargazers)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)\n![Shell](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Shell-4EAA25?logo=gnu-bash&logoColor=white)\n![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/-TypeScript-3178C6?logo=typescript&logoColor=white)\n![Go](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Go-00ADD8?logo=go&logoColor=white)\n![Markdown](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Markdown-000000?logo=markdown&logoColor=white)\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n**🌐 Language / 语言 / 語言**\n\n[**English**](README.md) | [简体中文](README.zh-CN.md) | [繁體中文](docs/zh-TW/README.md) | [日本語](docs/ja-JP/README.md)\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n**来自 Anthropic 黑客马拉松获胜者的完整 Claude Code 配置集合。**\n\n生产级代理、技能、钩子、命令、规则和 MCP 配置，经过 10 多个月构建真实产品的密集日常使用而演化。\n\n---\n\n## 指南\n\n这个仓库只包含原始代码。指南解释了一切。\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n<a href=\"https://x.com/affaanmustafa/status/2012378465664745795\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1a471488-59cc-425b-8345-5245c7efbcef\" alt=\"The Shorthand Guide to Everything Claude Code\" />\n</a>\n</td>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n<a href=\"https://x.com/affaanmustafa/status/2014040193557471352\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c9ca43bc-b149-427f-b551-af6840c368f0\" alt=\"The Longform Guide to Everything Claude Code\" />\n</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><b>精简指南</b><br/>设置、基础、理念。<b>先读这个。</b></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><b>详细指南</b><br/>Token 优化、内存持久化、评估、并行化。</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n| 主题 | 你将学到什么 |\n|-------|-------------------|\n| Token 优化 | 模型选择、系统提示精简、后台进程 |\n| 内存持久化 | 自动跨会话保存/加载上下文的钩子 |\n| 持续学习 | 从会话中自动提取模式到可重用的技能 |\n| 验证循环 | 检查点 vs 持续评估、评分器类型、pass@k 指标 |\n| 并行化 | Git worktrees、级联方法、何时扩展实例 |\n| 子代理编排 | 上下文问题、迭代检索模式 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n在 2 分钟内快速上手：\n\n### 第一步：安装插件\n\n```bash\n# 添加市场\n/plugin marketplace add affaan-m/everything-claude-code\n\n# 安装插件\n/plugin install everything-claude-code@everything-claude-code\n```\n\n### 第二步：安装规则（必需）\n\n> ⚠️ **重要提示：** Claude Code 插件无法自动分发 `rules`，需要手动安装：\n\n```bash"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":734,"aggregated":"# Everything Claude Code\n\n[![Stars](https://img.shields.io/github/stars/affaan-m/everything-claude-code?style=flat)](https://github.com/affaan-m/everything-claude-code/stargazers)\n[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/license-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)\n![Shell](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Shell-4EAA25?logo=gnu-bash&logoColor=white)\n![TypeScript](https://img.shields.io/badge/-TypeScript-3178C6?logo=typescript&logoColor=white)\n![Go](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Go-00ADD8?logo=go&logoColor=white)\n![Markdown](https://img.shields.io/badge/-Markdown-000000?logo=markdown&logoColor=white)\n\n---\n\n<div align=\"center\">\n\n**🌐 Language / 语言 / 語言**\n\n[**English**](README.md) | [简体中文](README.zh-CN.md) | [繁體中文](docs/zh-TW/README.md) | [日本語](docs/ja-JP/README.md)\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n**来自 Anthropic 黑客马拉松获胜者的完整 Claude Code 配置集合。**\n\n生产级代理、技能、钩子、命令、规则和 MCP 配置，经过 10 多个月构建真实产品的密集日常使用而演化。\n\n---\n\n## 指南\n\n这个仓库只包含原始代码。指南解释了一切。\n\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n<a href=\"https://x.com/affaanmustafa/status/2012378465664745795\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1a471488-59cc-425b-8345-5245c7efbcef\" alt=\"The Shorthand Guide to Everything Claude Code\" />\n</a>\n</td>\n<td width=\"50%\">\n<a href=\"https://x.com/affaanmustafa/status/2014040193557471352\">\n<img src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/c9ca43bc-b149-427f-b551-af6840c368f0\" alt=\"The Longform Guide to Everything Claude Code\" />\n</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td align=\"center\"><b>精简指南</b><br/>设置、基础、理念。<b>先读这个。</b></td>\n<td align=\"center\"><b>详细指南</b><br/>Token 优化、内存持久化、评估、并行化。</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n\n| 主题 | 你将学到什么 |\n|-------|-------------------|\n| Token 优化 | 模型选择、系统提示精简、后台进程 |\n| 内存持久化 | 自动跨会话保存/加载上下文的钩子 |\n| 持续学习 | 从会话中自动提取模式到可重用的技能 |\n| 验证循环 | 检查点 vs 持续评估、评分器类型、pass@k 指标 |\n| 并行化 | Git worktrees、级联方法、何时扩展实例 |\n| 子代理编排 | 上下文问题、迭代检索模式 |\n\n---\n\n## 🚀 快速开始\n\n在 2 分钟内快速上手：\n\n### 第一步：安装插件\n\n```bash\n# 添加市场\n/plugin marketplace add affaan-m/everything-claude-code\n\n# 安装插件\n/plugin install everything-claude-code@everything-claude-code\n```\n\n### 第二步：安装规则（必需）\n\n> ⚠️ **重要提示：** Claude Code 插件无法自动分发 `rules`，需要手动安装：\n\n```bash","cwd":"/Users/ling/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774114109683}}
{"type":"message","id":"2a3eb94e","parentId":"0e99a7d7","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:28:41.522Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I understand. This is the Everything Claude Code system (the same one we read about in the security audit). It's a comprehensive Claude Code configuration system that includes:\n- Rules (language-specific)\n- Skills\n- Commands\n- Hooks\n- MCP configs\n- Agents\n\nAnd importantly, it has a Claude Code plugin format (`@affaan-m/everything-claude-code`). It's designed for Claude Code, but we're using OpenClaw.\n\nThe key issue is: **this is designed for Claude Code, not OpenClaw**. While OpenClaw is inspired by/built on similar concepts, the installation methods may not be directly compatible.\n\nAlso, based on the security audit we read earlier (from the xu-xiang fork), there were significant security concerns about this ecosystem:\n\n\n- 12-20% of ClawdHub skills were malicious\n- Hidden prompt injection in skills\n- This is a comprehensive system that requires careful auditing\n\nBefore proceeding, I should clarify a few critical questions with the user: whether they want this specifically for Claude Code or OpenClaw, what specific components they want installed, and whether they've reviewed the security implications since this is their own fork. I should also note that a full system like this requires careful review before installation.\n\nActually, I already explained the security situation when they chose option A. The user picked \"A\" to install to OpenClaw workspace, but this system is really designed for Claude Code, not OpenClaw—different frameworks entirely. I need to be honest about this fundamental mismatch and ask what they're actually trying to accomplish.","thinkingSignature":"dbbb84c67b5c40cc4dde3ff7b1cf17a16cb27d6fa2dad27d2a84ddc2632f3194"},{"type":"text","text":"这个仓库是 **Everything Claude Code** 系统，安装方式是为 **Claude Code** 设计的（`/plugin` 命令），跟 **OpenClaw** 是不同框架，不能直接安装。\n\n需要先确认：\n\n### 你想达成什么具体效果？\n\n| 选项 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **①** | 你是想给 **Claude Code CLI** 用这套规则/技能系统？ |\n| **②** | 你是想把这套规则/技能迁移到 **OpenClaw** 里用？ |\n| **③** | 你是想参考这套规则，**手动复制部分 skill** 到 OpenClaw？ |\n\n告诉我目标，我帮你找到最适合的方式。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":106895,"output":464,"cacheRead":37752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":145111,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774114109712}}
