{"type":"message","id":"af39fff0","parentId":"2775ac82","timestamp":"2026-03-21T17:38:25.159Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works. The agent-browser CLI is working and can control the browser. Now I should explain to the user how they can use this with OpenClaw.","thinkingSignature":"7bb71bb02d339f366d828ed74ca9bba6a77e45b17229dc8c19f11ee53721d6cc"},{"type":"text","text":"\n✅ **agent-browser 安装成功！**\n\n测试结果：\n- 打开 example.com ✅\n- 获取页面结构（Accessibility Tree）✅\n\n### 如何在 OpenClaw 中使用\n\n通过 `exec` 调用：\n\n```bash\nagent-browser open https://example.com\nagent-browser snapshot\nagent-browser click \"button\"\nagent-browser type \"input\" \"text\"\n```\n\n### 可以在 OpenClaw 中做什么\n\n- 网页自动化任务\n- 数据抓取\n- 截图\n- 表单填写\n- UI 测试\n\n需要我帮你写个简单测试，或者把这个功能加到 OpenClaw 的 skill 里吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":127068,"output":162,"cacheRead":37752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":164982,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774114694338}}
